title: Naver Charts Its Own AI Path After Surprise Exit From Government Model Project

title: The US imposes 25% tariff on Nvidia’s H200 AI chips headed to China
description: After months of rumors that the Trump administration was going to impose tariffs on semiconductors, a tariff has been announced for some chips. The tariff only applies to certain semiconductors, including the Nvidia H200 advanced AI chips set to ship to China. Source link
